  "prompt": "What is the fee structure of Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam?",
  "response": "Sri Chaitanya schools have a varied fee structure that depends on several factors:\n\n*   **Specific Branch:** Fees vary significantly between different branches of Sri Chaitanya in Visakhapatnam.\n*   **Grade Level:** Fees increase as the student progresses to higher grades (e.g., Nursery, Classes 1-10, Intermediate/11-12).\n*   **Program/Curriculum:** The fee structure changes depending on the educational plan.\n*   **Hostel or Day Scholar:** Hostel fees are extra.\n\nYou must contact the specific Sri Chaitanya branch in Visakhapatnam you're interested in to get precise and up-to-date fee information. Here are some ways to find that information:\n\n*   **Visit the School Directly:** This is the best way to get detailed information about fees, payment schedules, and any available scholarships or discounts.\n*   **Call the School:** Look up the phone number of the specific Sri Chaitanya branch in Visakhapatnam online and call them.\n*   **Check the Sri Chaitanya Website:** While they might not list specific fees for each branch online, you might find contact information or an inquiry form you can use.",
